OL,3,CUK government takes 'first steps'
OL,4,Ctowards repealing and replacing Legacy
OL,5,CAct
OL,7,FThe Northern Ireland Secretary Hilary
OL,8,FBenn said the UK Government is taking
OL,9,Fthe "first steps" to honour its
OL,10,Fcommitment to repeal and replace
OL,11,Fcontroversial legacy legislation.
OL,13,FMaking a statement to the Commons on
OL,14,FWednesday, Mr Benn said: "The steps I
OL,15,Fam outlining today seek to correct the
OL,16,Fmistakes of the previous government's
OL,17,Fapproach, ensure compliance with the
OL,18,FECHR (European Convention on Human
OL,19,FRights) and deliver on what this
OL,20,FGovernment has promised.
