OL,5,CAct
OL,7,F"The removal of conditional immunity,
OL,8,Fthe reinstatement of legacy inquests
OL,9,Fhalted by the Act, restoring civil
OL,10,Fcases and reforming ICRIR (Independent
OL,11,FCommission for Reconciliation and
OL,12,FInformation Recovery) while enabling
OL,13,Fit to continue working on behalf of
OL,14,Fthe growing number of families who
OL,15,Fhave already sought its help."
