OL,5,CAct
OL,7,FMr Benn continued: "Part of the reason
OL,8,Fthat ICRIR does not currently command
OL,9,Fthe confidence from all survivors and
OL,10,Fvictims groups is because it was
OL,11,Fcreated in an Act that closed off any
OL,12,Fother route of remedy.
OL,14,F"People were told, 'you cannot have a
OL,15,Fcivil case. You can't have an inquest.
OL,16,FIf you're having an inquest now, we're
OL,17,Fcutting it short on the May 1 deadline
OL,18,Fand the only place you can go is
OL,19,Fthere'.
