OL,7,F"Well that damaged, if I may say so,
OL,8,Fit damaged confidence in ICRIR."
OL,10,FThe son of John Eagleson has welcomed
OL,11,Fthe announcement; his father was shot
OL,12,Fdead by the IRA in 1982.
OL,14,FConservative shadow Northern Ireland
OL,15,Fsecretary Alex Burghart told MPs
OL,16,FLabour has a "mandate" to change
OL,17,Flegacy legislation, but urged
OL,18,Fministers to "spare a thought" for
OL,19,Fveterans who may feel a sense of
OL,20,F"dread".
