OL,5,CAct
OL,7,FMr Burghart told the Commons: "The
OL,8,FLabour Party won a general election on
OL,9,Fa manifesto which included a number of
OL,10,Fmeasures which the Secretary of State
OL,11,Fhas just discussed and it has a
OL,12,Fmandate to make the changes it wants
OL,13,Fto make.
OL,15,F"But I will say this: there was an
OL,16,Fattempt by the last government, a
OL,17,Fdesire by the last government to draw
OL,18,Fa line under many difficult things
OL,19,Fthat have happened and with the
OL,20,Factions that the Government is now
OL,21,Ftaking, that line is being erased.
