OL,7,F"I'll remind the House of the central
OL,8,Freasons that the last government
OL,9,Flegislated for ` it did so to try and
OL,10,Fprotect some elderly people including
OL,11,Fservicemen who were being brought
OL,12,Fbefore inquests to discuss events that
OL,13,Fmay or may not have happened very many
OL,14,Fyears before."
