OL,7,FThe shadow Northern Ireland secretary
OL,8,Fadded: "Tonight, there will be many
OL,9,Fsuch men harbouring a sense of dread,
OL,10,Fand I know the Government is taking a
OL,11,Fdifferent approach, but I do ask them
OL,12,Fto spare a thought for those men this
OL,13,Fevening and to think very deeply about
OL,14,Fwhat it can do to support them."
